<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Attendance Alert</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #0A0A0A;
            background-color: #FFFFFF;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .header {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 40px 0;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #E5E5E5;
        }
        .logo {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #171717;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 40px 0;
        }
        .page-title {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #171717;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .alert-type-badge {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #FEF3C7;
            color: #92400E;
            padding: 4px 14px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            font-size: 12px;
            font-weight: 600;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .alert-info {
            background-color: #F5F5F5;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .info-row {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            padding-bottom: 10px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #E5E5E5;
        }
        .info-row:last-child {
            margin-bottom: 0;
            padding-bottom: 0;
            border-bottom: none;
        }
        .info-label {
            font-weight: 500;
            color: #737373;
        }
        .info-value {
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #171717;
        }
        .alert-message {
            background-color: #FEF3C7;
            border: 1px solid #F59E0B;
            padding: 16px;
            border-radius: 6px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            color: #92400E;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        .cta-button {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #171717;
            color: #FAFAFA;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 6px;
            font-weight: 500;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .policy-note {
            background-color: #F5F5F5;
            padding: 16px;
            border-radius: 6px;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #525252;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px 0;
            border-top: 1px solid #E5E5E5;
            color: #737373;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <div class="logo">Employee Management System</div>
        </div>

        <div class="content">
            <h1 class="page-title">Attendance Alert</h1>
            <div><span class="alert-type-badge">{{alertType}}</span></div>

            <p>Dear {{employeeName}},</p>

            <p>An attendance irregularity has been recorded for your profile. Please review the details below and take the necessary action.</p>

            <div class="alert-info">
                <div class="info-row">
                    <span class="info-label">Employee:</span>
                    <span class="info-value">{{employeeName}}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="info-row">
                    <span class="info-label">Date:</span>
                    <span class="info-value">{{date}}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="info-row">
                    <span class="info-label">Alert Type:</span>
                    <span class="info-value">{{alertType}}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="info-row">
                    <span class="info-label">Reported To:</span>
                    <span class="info-value">{{managerName}}</span>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="alert-message">
                <strong>Please Note:</strong> This alert has been shared with your reporting manager, <strong>{{managerName}}</strong>. If this was due to an emergency or approved reason, please provide an explanation through the portal or contact HR directly.
            </div>

            <a href="{{actionUrl}}" class="cta-button">Review &amp; Respond</a>

            <div class="policy-note">
                Consistent attendance is important for team operations. Repeated alerts may be reviewed during your performance evaluation. Please reach out to your manager or HR if you need any support.
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
            <p>This is an automated message from the Employee Management System.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
